(186, '_transient_dash_4077549d03da2e451c8b5f002294ff51', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2015/08/billie/''>WordPress 4.3 “Billie”</a> <span class="rss-date">18 sierpnia 2015</span><div class="rssSummary">Version 4.3 of WordPress, named “Billie” in honor of jazz singer Billie Holiday, is available for download or update in your WordPress dashboard. New features in 4.3 make it even easier to format your content and customize your site. Menus in the Customizer Create your menu, update it, and assign it, all while live-previewing in [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/the-wordpress-foundation-begins-accepting-applications-for-the-kim-parsell-memorial-scholarship''>WPTavern: The WordPress Foundation Begins Accepting Applications for the Kim Parsell Memorial Scholarship</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/hybrid-core-3-0-experiments-with-community-driven-documentation''>WPTavern: Hybrid Core 3.0 Experiments With Community-driven Documentation</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://ma.tt/2015/08/1-6m-downloads-in-23-hours/''>Matt: 1.6m Downloads in 23 Hours</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Popularna wtyczka:</span> <a href=''http://wordpress.org/plugins/siteorigin-panels/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>Page Builder by SiteOrigin</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=siteorigin-panels&amp;_wpnonce=a1442a830f&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Page Builder by SiteOrigin''>Zainstaluj</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
